n><hr size=1> Hafling race bonus is 10%, still in effect.  The Rogue exp modifier is 9.05 (compaired to 10 for base) and is also still in effect.  The exp penalties were removed for hybrids, but the exp bonuses for Warriors/Rogues remain.<br>
<br>
Oh, and there is a exp penality for Barbarians.  10.5 (if I remember correctly).  I havn't heard anything about a Vah Shir Bonus/Penality.<br>
