<br>
Racial:<br>
<br>
Halfling: 95<br>
Barbarian: 105<br>
Ogre: 115<br>
Troll: 120<br>
Iksar: 120<br>
All other races: 100<br>
<br>
Class:<br>
<br>
Rogue: 9.05<br>
Warrior: 9<br>
All other classes: 10<br>
(note: prior to the patch that changed the exp penalties for certain classes, some of the class penalties were as much as 14, but now, none are higher than 10).<br>
